manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The New Chapter Difference Nutrition for Every Woman Our hard-working, super-convenient, one-daily women's multivitamins are designed to enhance your holistic health. We’ve got you covered with the 20+ essential vitamins and minerals you need every day for immune, energy, stress, and beauty support, as well as heart, brain, bone, digestive, and breast health support.* Absorb The Good Stuff New Chapter multivitamins are expertly formulated for absorption—because you have to absorb nutrients to get their benefits! We fine-tune the levels of each vitamin & mineral, choose ingredients that work best with the body, and ferment key nutrients with probiotics and whole foods. This process helps your body recognize our vitamins as food so you can get their full benefits and feel your best. Because Quality Matters Our carefully crafted multivitamins use only the highest quality ingredients, including superfoods like organic Turmeric, Elderberry, and Maca. Since 1982, we've been going the extra mile to bring you the best possible nutrition that your body can actually absorb.

People & Planet We travel the globe to build relationships with partners who share our commitment to sustainable sourcing. Knowing our suppliers and the origins of their crops helps us uphold an environmentally sound supply chain. New Chapter suppliers follow a written code of conduct—a clear set of principles that cover sustainability, human rights and fair working conditions, wage and hour practices, and non-discrimination. New Chapter is growing the organic movement by funding vital research in regenerative organic farming—practices that will heal the soil, repair global food security, and start to reverse climate change. We compost, recycle, or reuse more than 80% of the waste we produce – everything from lunch leftovers and office paper to pallets and shrink-wrap. New Chapter is also a Zero Manufacturing Waste to Landfill facility.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent for vegans and non-vegans alike! However…
